{"tid":1463832,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"依個局set得靚呢！","createTime":"2019-08-13T13:52:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T15:10:29.000Z","uid":292213,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c20e7a0f5fce4c378f2adbe7b685f620a595d361","tid":1463832,"uid":292213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:52:16.000Z","msg":"昨日，差佬<strong>安排</strong>一大炸狗車、狗隻在外圍stand by，機場裡面的人，立刻冷靜和平離開！<br />\n<br />\n今日，差佬<strong>冇安排</strong>，狗和狗車&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n如果機場有<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">發生任何一事</span></span>！<br />\n(包括 和旅客衝突 其他人身體碰 旅客對香港人投訴 甚至搵個大陸人扮暈咗死咗)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所有示威者，都<span style=\"color: red;\">跌落這個局</span>裡面！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">示威者是需要警察維持秩序呢！！！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n以後&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">示威者 成為失控的代表</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">警察 成為維持秩序的代表</span><br />\n<br />\n這個局林鄭靚set呢！！<br />\n<br />\n-----------------<br />\n核彈都唔割<br />\n冷靜分析 焦中目標<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"6c006bc58619237941adfde43f63016bd3cd6c40","tid":1463832,"uid":292213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:54:02.000Z","msg":"努力推下，希望唔好中林鄭計"},{"pid":"f55876ab1ec75983759fd21a34c5125e8b804bfc","tid":1463832,"uid":292213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:56:08.000Z","msg":"我只是C9！<br />\n明白&hellip;失民意失江山<br />\n<br />\n我地需要更多人撐我地呢"},{"pid":"11951e69d6c704ad7fa2628db4a6a05a808f6e0a","tid":1463832,"uid":294974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:56:50.000Z","msg":"同意<br />\n----------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n如果覺得講得啱，唔該睇睇同幫推唔該<br />\np牌仔嘅野冇人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n(話我鬼都要講㗎喇)佔機場唔係無撚敵㗎，屌<b